data.content:
Looking at [src/dev/extra-styles.css](src/dev/extra-styles.css):

**OKLCH:** ✅ Yes, refactored to OKLCH color space:
```css
--local-oklch-blue-300: oklch(0.78 0.090 265);
--local-oklch-blue-350: oklch(0.74 0.105 265);
--local-oklch-blue-400: oklch(0.69 0.120 265);
--local-oklch-blue-500: oklch(0.60 0.145 265);
--local-oklch-blue-600: oklch(0.51 0.165 265);
```

**CIELAB:** ❌ No, still using hex values:
```css
--local-cielab-blue-300: #AAC4EE;
--local-cielab-blue-350: #96B5EA;
--local-cielab-blue-400: #80A6E6;
--local-cielab-blue-500: #5589DD;
--local-cielab-blue-600: #2B6BD5;
